KEEP IT SHARP  Troubleshooting

THE ROUTINE  Your repeatable weekly workflow

Here’s how the engine runs once it’s built. Total hands-on time: roughly one hour a week.

DO IT NOW  Quick-start checklist

Open claude.ai/customize

Click Skills to open your skill workspace

Click + → Browse skills to see what’s available

Visit github.com/coreyhaines31/marketingskills and download 3–5 skills

Add each skill: + → Create skill → paste the content

Write your 6 context files and upload them

Run the master prompt and review the batch

Schedule, publish, and repeat the weekly routine